&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://g-issues.chromium.org/issues/40635377"&gt;https://g-issues.chromium.org/issues/40635377&lt;/a&gt;&gt;, which has some discussions 
around the `unadjustedMovement` flag support on Linux &amp; other platforms.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

For the other tests, I couldn't manage to find much context around them 
unfortunately.

