&lt;pre&gt;On Mon, Dec 15, 2025 at 6:25 PM Chris Harrelson &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e88b809a819bc6c6c6a88b809a8785819d85c6879a8f"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
