On Mon, Dec 15, 2025 at 5:40 PM Reilly Grant &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="8af8efe3e6a4a4a4cae9e2f8e5e7e3ffe7a4e5f8ed"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

