&lt;div class="msgHead"&gt; &lt;h1&gt; &lt;span class="subject"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=subject:%22Re%5C%3A+%5C%5Bblink%5C-dev%5C%5D+Intent+to+Prototype+%5C%26+Ship%5C%3A+trigger%5C-scope%22&amp;o=newest" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Re: [blink-dev] Intent to Prototype & Ship: trigger-scope&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p class="darkgray font13"&gt; &lt;span class="sender pipe"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=from:%22Mike+Taylor%22" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Mike Taylor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20251217" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 17 Dec 2025 08:13:40 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div itemprop="articleBody" class="msgBody"&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;Oh, it was just pointed out that the spec is essentially &quot;TODO: spec &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;this&quot; (at least that's my read on the second Note). &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
