&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; caret-eol-001.html caret-eol-002.html caret-eol-003.html
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; caret-eol-004.tentative.html.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://wpt.fyi/results/css/css-ui?label=experimental&amp;label=master&amp;aligned"&gt;https://wpt.fyi/results/css/css-ui?label=experimental&amp;label=master&amp;aligned&lt;/a&gt;,
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; in case others want to see the results at a quick glance.
