&gt; *Design docs*
&gt;
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1WpTAK_UViXL84YBR-4Hsj2y_YPwh3QZBqpB3KB3Xh0s/edit?resourcekey=0-P-jSRgKuk1vOTwOY15DnCQ&amp;tab=t.0#heading=h.bat9awopsp53"&gt;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1WpTAK_UViXL84YBR-4Hsj2y_YPwh3QZBqpB3KB3Xh0s/edit?resourcekey=0-P-jSRgKuk1vOTwOY15DnCQ&amp;tab=t.0#heading=h.bat9awopsp53&lt;/a&gt;
